              <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">All our golf carts are professionally maintained and regularly serviced to ensure reliable performance for all your Halloween activities.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          
          <div class="group flex items-start hover:bg-white p-6 rounded-2xl transition-all duration-300">
            <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-gradient-to-br from-orange-100 to-orange-200 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center mr-6 mt-1 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-300">
              <i class="fa-solid fa-gas-pump text-orange-600 text-xl"></i>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3">Gas-Powered Reliability</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">Our gas-powered golf carts provide reliable performance for all your Halloween activities, with no battery concerns during long events.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          
          <div class="group flex items-start hover:bg-white p-6 rounded-2xl transition-all duration-300">
